#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellipkinc.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.ellipkinc"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:1 of
msgid "Incomplete elliptic integral of the first kind"
msgstr "第一类不完全椭圆积分"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:3 of
msgid "This function is defined as"
msgstr "该函数定义为"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:5 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"K(\\phi, m) = \\int_0^{\\phi} [1 - m \\sin(t)^2]^{-1/2} dt\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:7 of
msgid "This function is also called :math:`F(\\phi, m)`."
msgstr "该函数也称为 :math:`F(\\phi, m)`。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellipkinc.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:9 of
msgid "amplitude of the elliptic integral"
msgstr "椭圆积分的幅度"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:11 of
msgid "parameter of the elliptic integral"
msgstr "椭圆积分的参数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:13 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function values"
msgstr "函数值的可选输出数组"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellipkinc.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:16 of
msgid "**K** -- Value of the elliptic integral"
msgstr "**K** -- 椭圆积分的值"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellipkinc.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ellipkm1`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:22 of
msgid "Complete elliptic integral of the first kind, near `m` = 1"
msgstr "`m` = 1 附近的完整第一类椭圆积分"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ellipk`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:25 of
msgid "Complete elliptic integral of the first kind"
msgstr "完整的第一类椭圆积分"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:27 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ellipe`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:28 of
msgid "Complete elliptic integral of the second kind"
msgstr "完整第二类椭圆积分"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:30 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ellipeinc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:31 of
msgid "Incomplete elliptic integral of the second kind"
msgstr "第二类不完全椭圆积分"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprf`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:34 of
msgid "Completely-symmetric elliptic integral of the first kind."
msgstr "完全对称的第一类椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:37 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:38 of
msgid ""
"Wrapper for the Cephes [1]_ routine `ellik`.  The computation is carried "
"out using the arithmetic-geometric mean algorithm."
msgstr "Cephes [1]_ 例程 `ellik` 的封装。计算使用算术-几何平均算法进行。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:41 of
msgid ""
"The parameterization in terms of :math:`m` follows that of section 17.2 "
"in [2]_. Other parameterizations in terms of the complementary parameter "
":math:`1 - m`, modular angle :math:`\\sin^2(\\alpha) = m`, or modulus "
":math:`k^2 = m` are also used, so be careful that you choose the correct "
"parameter."
msgstr ""
"以 :math:`m` 为参数的参数化遵循 [2]_ 中第 17.2 节的定义。其他参数化方式"
"包括互补参数 :math:`1 - m`，模角 :math:`\\sin^2(\\alpha) = m`，或模数 :"
"math:`k^2 = m`，因此请确保选择正确的参数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:47 of
msgid ""
"The Legendre K incomplete integral (or F integral) is related to "
"Carlson's symmetric R_F function [3]_. Setting :math:`c = \\csc^2\\phi`,"
msgstr ""
"Legendre K 不完全积分（或 F 积分）与 Carlson 的对称 R_F 函数 [3]_ 相关。"
"设 :math:`c = \\csc^2\\phi`，"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipkinc:51 of
msgid ""
"F(\\phi, m) = R_F(c-1, c-k^2, c) .\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

